<h1>泰国总理候选人皮塔·林家伦拉是谁？</h1>
<p>Author: 半岛电视台</p>
<p>Publisher: Al Jazeera</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-07-13T10:57:38</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-07-13T10:57:38</p>
